Több időzítőhőz:

Public WithEvents Timer1 as Timer
Then in Class_Initialize()

Timer1.Interval = 100 ' or what ever you wish
Timer1.Enabled = True

variable is declared withevents so you can now call and handle Timer event.

Private Sub Timer1_Timer()

' Your Code Goes Here

End Sub

